{
  "id": "019cdcdc-fd01-7d11-b0d7-b5f020f95a8b",
  "content": "## Architecture\n\n### Crate Placement\n\n| Component | Crate | Rationale |\n|-----------|-------|-----------|\n| `ChunkingStrategy` trait | `corvia-kernel` | Universal contract, like `Retriever`/`Augmenter` |\n| `ChunkingPipeline` | `corvia-kernel` | Kernel orchestrator between adapter and embedding |\n| `FormatRegistry` | `corvia-kernel` | Auto-detect + adapter overrides |\n| `ChunkingConfig` | `corvia-common` | TOML-configurable parameters |\n| `AstChunker` | `corvia-adapter-git` | Keeps tree-sitter deps in adapter crate |\n| `MarkdownChunker` | `corvia-kernel` | No special deps, broadly useful |\n| `ConfigChunker` | `corvia-kernel` | Uses existing serde deps |\n| `PdfChunker` | `corvia-kernel` | PDF text extraction (feature-gated if heavy) |\n| `FallbackChunker` | `corvia-kernel` | Recursive text splitting, zero deps |\n\n\n### New Files\n\n```\ncrates/corvia-kernel/src/\n  chunking_pipeline.rs     — ChunkingPipeline, FormatRegistry, ProcessingReport\n  chunking_strategy.rs     — ChunkingStrategy trait, RawChunk, ProcessedChunk, SourceFile types\n  chunking_markdown.rs     — MarkdownChunker\n  chunking_config_fmt.rs   — ConfigChunker (TOML/YAML/JSON)\n  chunking_pdf.rs          — PdfChunker\n  chunking_fallback.rs     — FallbackChunker\n\ncrates/corvia-common/src/\n  config.rs                — add ChunkingConfig section\n\ncorvia-adapter-git/src/\n  ast_chunker.rs           — AstChunker (migrated from treesitter.rs, implements ChunkingStrategy)\n  treesitter.rs            — retained as internal parsing module used by AstChunker\n```\n",
  "source_version": "docs/rfcs/2026-03-02-m3.3-embedding-chunking-design.md",
